\c 32
\s1 Jacob sent gifts to Esau as he prepared to meet him
\p 
\v 1 \w As|strong="H1121"\w* Jacob \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w his|strong="H7725"\w* family continued traveling, \w some|strong="H4725"\w* angels, whom God \w sent|strong="H7725"\w*, met \w him|strong="H7725"\w*.
