\v 3 \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w* told \w some|strong="H4725"\w* \w of|strong="H8034"\w* \w the|strong="H7200"\w* \w men|strong="H4264"\w* \w to|strong="H7121"\w* go ahead \w of|strong="H8034"\w* \w him|strong="H7121"\w* \w to|strong="H7121"\w* \w his|strong="H7121"\w* older brother Esau, \w who|strong="H1931"\w* \w was|strong="H8034"\w* living \w in|strong="H8034"\w* Seir, \w the|strong="H7200"\w* \w land|strong="H4725"\w* \w where|strong="H4725"\w* \w the|strong="H7200"\w* descendants \w of|strong="H8034"\w* Edom lived.
