\v 13 \w Jacob|strong="H5608"\w* slept \w there|strong="H7230"\w* \w that|strong="H3808"\w* night. \w The|strong="H7760"\w* next morning \w he|strong="H3808"\w* selected some animals \w to|strong="H3220"\w* \w give|strong="H7760"\w* \w to|strong="H3220"\w* \w his|strong="H7760"\w* brother Esau.
