\s1 The descendants of Esau
\p 
\v 1 ◄Here \w is|strong="H1931"\w*/\w I|strong="H6215"\w* \w will|strong="H1931"\w* now give you► \w a|strong="H3068"\w* list \w of|strong="H8435"\w* \w the|strong="H1931"\w* descendants \w of|strong="H8435"\w* \w Esau|strong="H6215"\w*, whose other name \w was|strong="H1931"\w* Edom.
